          <title>
            <string language="en">Women's ACC Basketball Tournament School Day Curriculum</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Basketball-Turnier-Schule-Tageslehrplan 
AKKUMULATOR Der Frauen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Programme d'études de Jour D'École de Tournoi De
Basket-ball de l'ACCUMULATEUR des Femmes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Curriculum Do Dia Da Escola Do Tournament Do 
Basketball do ACUMULADOR Das Mulheres</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Programma di studi Di Giorno Della Scuola Di 
Torneo Di Pallacanestro dell'ACCUMULATORE Delle Donne</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Πρόγραμμα σπουδών σχολικής ημέρας πρωταθλημάτων 
καλαθοσφαίρισης της ACC γυναικών</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Plan de estudios Del Día De la Escuela Del Torneo
Del Baloncesto del ACUMULADOR De las Mujeres</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Four collections of basketball-based units for grades K-8 teach all areas of the curriculum through the lens of the 2007 Women's Atlantic Coast Conference (ACC) basketball tournament.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Humanities</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Vier Ansammlungen der Basketball-gegründeten 
Maßeinheiten für Grade K-8 unterrichten alle Bereiche des Lehrplans 
durch das Objektiv des 2007 der Küste-Konferenz der Frauen 
atlantischen Basketballturniers (AKKUMULATOR).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Quatre collections d'unités basket-ball-basées 
pour les catégories K-8 enseignent toutes les zones du programme 
d'études par l'objectif des 2007 du tournoi atlantique de basket-ball
de conférence de la côte femmes (ACCUMULATEUR).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Quatro coleções de unidades basketball-baseadas 
para as classes K-8 ensinam todas as áreas do curriculum através da 
lente do tournament atlantic do basketball da conferência da costa 
das 2007 mulheres (ACUMULADOR).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Quattro collezioni di unità pallacanestro-basate 
per i gradi K-8 insegnano tutte le zone del programma di studi tramite
l'obiettivo del torneo atlantico di pallacanestro di congresso del 
litorale delle 2007 donne (ACCUMULATORE).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τέσσερις συλλογές των καλαθοσφαίριση-βασισμένων στην 
μονάδων για τους βαθμούς Κ-8 διδάσκουν όλους τους τομείς του 
προγράμματος σπουδών μέσω του φακού των ατλαντικών πρωταθλημάτων
καλαθοσφαίρισης διασκέψεων ακτών των 2007 γυναικών (ACC).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Cuatro colecciones de las unidades 
baloncesto-basadas para los grados K-8 enseñan todas las áreas del 
plan de estudios a través de la lente del torneo atlántico del 
baloncesto de la conferencia de la costa de las 2007 mujeres 
(ACUMULADOR).</string>
          </description>
